history.content:
E-commerce is probably a familiar term, but trends and roles in e-commerce are ever-changing. The Alpha Mu pledge class of Alpha Kappa Psi, a professional business fraternity, is incredibly excited to present “The Modern Marketplace”, a professional forum focused on the increasing popularity and prevalence of e-commerce and digital transactions. Join us on April 5th at 6:30 PM to meet representatives from top companies including Amazon, Venmo, PayPal, Salesforce, Kickstarter, and many others, who will be speaking about their professional experiences and industry insights. The event consists of individual speaker presentations, a facilitated panel, audience Q&A, and a networking session at the end. Resumes will be accepted, and free Chipotle will be served!

For more information: https://www.facebook.com/events/1549942665305625/
history.subject: E-commerce Professional Forum with Amazon, Paypal, Kickstarter! Resume Drop & Free Food!
